Clinton Urges Syria Allies to Get on ‘Right Side of History’

-- B y   D a v i d   L e r m a n
-- 
2011-08-12T15:44:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-12/clinton-urges-syria-allies-to-get-on-right-side-of-history-.html
Secretary of State  Hillary Clinton 
today urged nations doing business with  Syria  to “get on the
right side of history” and condemn the regime’s violent
repression of dissent.  The world should stop buying Syrian oil, Clinton said at
the State Department in  Washington . She cited a “crescendo of
condemnation” of the regime of Bashar al-Assad.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Lerman in Washington at 
 dlerman1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Steven Komarow at 
 skomarow1@bloomberg.net  